====Return to the Brownstone====
[[File:MDillardSugar-BurnedBrownstone.jpg|{{AltFloat}}|Dillard being taken back to her [[Mariah Dillard's Brownstone|Brownstone]]]]
{{Quote|Yes, yes, I'm scared! I got no [[Mariah Dillard's Brownstone|home]]! I got no [[Harlem's Paradise|club]]! [[Bushmaster]], [[New York City Police Department|cops]], [[Luke Cage]], everybody is up my ass! Yes, I'm scared, because it's over!"<br>"What's over? What are you gonna do? Gonna buy your little house upstate? You gonna buy a food truck? Look at me. The second you pushed [[Cottonmouth|Cornell]] through that window, you became a gangster.|Mariah Dillard and [[Shades]]|If It Ain't Rough, It Ain't Right}}
