{{Quote|It already seems like a lifetime ago, I can't even keep my own family together."<br>"Kids, they ain't easy."<br>"I wasn't there for [[Tilda Johnson|Tilda]] when she was growing up, I thought I could make up for lost time."<br>"I was there for [[Luke Cage|Carl]] growing, but I wasn't really there.|Mariah Dillard and [[James Lucas]]|For Pete's Sake}}
