==Trivia==
*In the comics, Black Mariah is the leader of the [[w:c:marvel:Rat Pack (Black Mariah)|Rat Pack]], a [[New York City|New York]] street gang. Her name is a reference to the classic nicknamed used for the {{WPS|Police van#Black Maria|police van}} in Harlem.

